definitions.definition: A place in Texas , United States :

subdefinitions.definition: A coastal city , the county seat of Galveston County , Texas , United States , located on Galveston Island and Pelican Island .
Ellipsis of Galveston Island : an island of Galveston county, Galveston city, Texas , United States ; an a barrier island separating in Galveston bay and the Gulf of Mexico , Atlantic Ocean .
Ellipsis of Port of Galveston : a port in Galveston island, Galveston city, Galveston county, Texas , United States .
Ellipsis of Galveston County : a county of Texas , United States . County seat: Galveston .
Ellipsis of Galveston Bay Area : a region of Texas , United States , surrounding Galveston Bay , on the Gulf of Mexico , Atlantic .
Ellipsis of Galveston Bay : a bay of the Gulf of Mexico , Atlantic in Texas , United States .

definitions.definition: A town in Jackson Township, Cass County , Indiana , United States , named after Galveston, Texas.
An unincorporated community in Pittsylvania County , Virginia , United States , named after Galveston, Texas
